Tibet Province with 2000 Population Census Data From 9.95% Long Form Data (table L1-L4) is a polygon theme representinfg Tibet Provice China in 2000.   Attribute information includes a variety of variables from the long form data from the 2000 Chinese census.  

This data layer is part of the Tibet 2000 Township Census data set produced by the All China Marketing Research Co. and distributed by the University of Michigan, China Data Center.
